    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://github.com/dotnet/interactive/pull/1451</guid>
      <link>https://github.com/dotnet/interactive/pull/1451</link>
      <title>PR: add `JupyterInteractiveHost` - @brettfo</title>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This adds a jupyter interactive host like we already have for vscode, which means from either environment and from C#, F#, or PowerShell you can do:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;C#:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="language-csharp"&gt;var value = await InteractiveHost.GetInputAsync();
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;F#:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp"&gt;let value = InteractiveHost.GetInputAsync().Result
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pwsh:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="language-pwsh"&gt;$value = Read-Host
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Jun 2021 21:27:36 Z</pubDate>
    </item>
